3
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:34,390
Sima Jiao, a barrier in this mountain suppresses you.

4
00:00:34,390 --> 00:00:39,700
The Eight Great Palaces sealed you here and took your place to rule the Immortal Mansion.

5
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:41,600
You are trapped with no way out.

6
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:44,470
How can you possibly change your fate?

7
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:51,120
Those hypocrites...

8
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:54,730
locked me in this lightless prison,

9
00:00:55,990 --> 00:00:58,820
hoping I would yield.

10
00:01:01,060 --> 00:01:04,600
But I have forged the Spirit Fire's avatar.

11
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:07,880
On the night of the new moon,

12
00:01:09,190 --> 00:01:11,060
this mountain...

13
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:14,340
will no longer bind me.

14
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:19,480
Now,

15
00:01:20,110 --> 00:01:22,520
I need only one last piece...

16
00:01:23,270 --> 00:01:25,890
to turn the game around and change my fate.

