265
00:20:32,790 --> 00:20:34,740
How bold.

266
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:51,120
Those people are too brave.

267
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:53,400
They couldn't leave, so they followed a snake.

268
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:56,170
Good thing this world has no clock in system.

269
00:20:56,170 --> 00:20:59,150
No one will notice I've skipped out.

270
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:10,040
What the...

271
00:21:14,990 --> 00:21:18,790
Demonic energy? So, she's from the Demon Realm.

272
00:21:18,790 --> 00:21:21,760
Who's there? I can see you.

273
00:21:25,510 --> 00:21:27,970
Clueless fool.

274
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:52,580
This is too creepy. I am going back.

275
00:22:09,360 --> 00:22:10,940
Let's go in.

276
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:23,870
In horror movies, the first to die is always the one alone.

277
00:22:23,870 --> 00:22:26,240
I should stay with the group.

278
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:05,750
The tower is so tall.

279
00:23:05,750 --> 00:23:08,450
But there isn't even an elevator?

280
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,760
- Blood!
- Blood!

281
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:13,140
What a bunch of fools.

282
00:24:14,070 --> 00:24:16,270
Greetings, Grandmaster.

283
00:24:16,270 --> 00:24:19,110
- Greetings, Grandmaster!
- Greetings, Grandmaster!

284
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:39,960
The Grandmaster's feet are incredibly well-cared-for.

285
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:41,920
So smooth and soft.

286
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:44,520
I wonder if his face is the same.

287
00:25:30,550 --> 00:25:36,170
This centuries-old Grandmaster is actually a pretty boy?

288
00:26:07,710 --> 00:26:09,280
You.

289
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:12,230
Why have you come here?

290
00:26:12,230 --> 00:26:15,680
I wish to serve you, Grandmaster.

291
00:26:17,230 --> 00:26:19,000
Liar.

292
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:27,360
How can someone so fair-skinned have such a bad temper?

293
00:26:27,360 --> 00:26:30,560
He's like a landmine ready to explode.

294
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:38,220
Do not come near me.

295
00:26:53,470 --> 00:26:57,090
You. What is your name?

296
00:26:57,990 --> 00:27:00,840
I am Wan Ling. I worship you, Grandmaster,

297
00:27:00,840 --> 00:27:02,980
and wish to serve you.

298
00:27:08,600 --> 00:27:11,200
That wasn't Junior Sister Wan Ling. Who was she?

299
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:13,120
How dare she enter disguised as Wan Ling?

300
00:27:13,120 --> 00:27:15,350
What did she want?

301
00:27:20,070 --> 00:27:22,470
He seems to be looking at me.

302
00:27:22,470 --> 00:27:25,680
Please, Grandmaster, just ignore me.

303
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:28,030
Here is someone even bolder.

304
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:30,550
How am I bold?

305
00:27:30,550 --> 00:27:34,900
I have done nothing, Grandmaster.

306
00:27:38,470 --> 00:27:40,210
Look at me.

307
00:27:49,030 --> 00:27:51,620
Open your eyes and look at me.

308
00:27:54,120 --> 00:27:57,240
You're still trying to play tricks?

309
00:27:58,470 --> 00:28:00,950
I've done nothing, Grandmaster.

310
00:28:03,060 --> 00:28:05,140
The Spirit Fire...

311
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:21,180
All of you, get out.

312
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:29,340
Out!

313
00:28:39,990 --> 00:28:42,880
The Grandmaster seems to have lost his mind.

314
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:44,750
In fact, he's pure madness!

315
00:28:44,750 --> 00:28:49,730
I suspect he let us in just to stock up on fresh meat

316
00:28:49,730 --> 00:28:51,690
for his pet snake.

317
00:28:51,690 --> 00:28:53,400
Nonsense.

318
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:54,600
The meeting with the Grandmaster is over for today.

319
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:58,290
We should find a place to rest and wait for his orders.

320
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:01,000
Let's go.

321
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:04,710
That Mu Nisheng from the Heaven Palace

322
00:29:04,710 --> 00:29:06,580
acts like everyone has to obey her.

323
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:08,430
Well, I will not.

324
00:29:08,430 --> 00:29:10,730
Let's go this way.

325
00:29:13,120 --> 00:29:17,400
Looks like these palace schemers aren't impressed with me.

326
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:20,030
Good. The less I stand out, the better.

327
00:29:20,030 --> 00:29:22,630
I just want to make it out alive.

328
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:25,750
We've walked for so long.

329
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:28,590
I think my feet are blistering.

330
00:29:38,230 --> 00:29:41,030
Sima Jiao actually spared her in the hall.

331
00:29:41,030 --> 00:29:43,560
What is so special about her?

332
00:29:48,470 --> 00:29:51,360
I hope the Grandmaster does not hold regular meetings

333
00:29:51,360 --> 00:29:53,310
and will not see me again.

334
00:29:53,310 --> 00:29:55,170
My feet hurt.

335
00:29:58,790 --> 00:30:00,680
Let me help you.

336
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:09,900
They stopped hurting.

337
00:30:10,710 --> 00:30:11,960
Thank you.

338
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:14,200
I'm Liao Tingyan. What's your name?

339
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:15,960
I am Ye Ruling.

340
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:17,880
Ruling.

341
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:22,070
Why are you alone, too?

342
00:30:22,070 --> 00:30:25,640
Are you, like me, from the "Doing Minimum Realm"?

343
00:30:25,640 --> 00:30:27,480
"Doing Minimum Realm"?

344
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:31,510
Is she referring to the Demon Realm?

345
00:30:31,510 --> 00:30:34,880
Which branch is the "Doing Minimum Realm"?

346
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:38,310
I just mean I do not want to serve the Grandmaster.

347
00:30:38,310 --> 00:30:40,120
I am a disciple of the Yin Palace.

348
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:43,000
My palace master sent me here.

349
00:30:46,120 --> 00:30:49,510
Why do you not want to serve the Grandmaster?

350
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:53,160
The entire Gengchen Immortal Mansion is sustained by his spiritual energy.

351
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:55,680
If you can gain his favor,

352
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:57,710
your cultivation will improve greatly.

353
00:30:57,710 --> 00:31:01,790
In a short time, you could achieve a millennium of bitter training.

354
00:31:01,790 --> 00:31:03,920
I have no such ambition.

355
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:07,860
I just want good food, good sleep, and to stay alive.

356
00:31:08,750 --> 00:31:10,990
Then what is your plan?

357
00:31:10,990 --> 00:31:14,550
I plan to find a sunny spot

358
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:17,270
where I can nap in the sun at midday and stay there.

359
00:31:17,270 --> 00:31:18,990
Do you want to join me?

360
00:31:18,990 --> 00:31:20,580
No.

361
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:26,600
But if you need help, you can come to the back hall to find me.

362
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:27,750
Goodbye.

363
00:31:27,750 --> 00:31:29,540
Thank you.

364
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:47,080
Liao Tingyan.

365
00:31:51,030 --> 00:31:53,360
Liao Tingyan has entered the mountain safely.

366
00:31:53,360 --> 00:31:55,400
Well done, Young Master.

367
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:57,760
You must have put in quite some effort.

368
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:01,360
I placed a spell on her beforehand to make sure

369
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:03,400
she could gain spiritual energy

370
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:06,470
from Yue Chuhui without anyone noticing during the selection.

371
00:32:06,470 --> 00:32:09,710
Good. Once she kills Sima Jiao,

372
00:32:09,710 --> 00:32:12,680
the Immortal-Demon Barrier will vanish,

373
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:16,290
and we of the Demon Realm will no longer be trapped in this desolate place.

374
00:32:16,290 --> 00:32:20,160
When that time comes, you had better keep your promise.

375
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:22,840
Rest assured. Once Sima Jiao is dead,

376
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:25,120
