377
00:32:25,120 --> 00:32:27,790
The disciples only entered today, yet a life lamp has already gone out.

378
00:32:27,790 --> 00:32:29,990
With the Grandmaster's ruthlessness

379
00:32:29,990 --> 00:32:32,120
and merciless nature,

380
00:32:32,120 --> 00:32:33,750
I fear he will...

381
00:32:33,750 --> 00:32:36,640
It is understandable that he would act that way.

382
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:37,920
500 years ago,

383
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:41,000
Sima Shi went mad and burned White Deer Cliff,

384
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:44,560
